---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kichijoji Jazz Adventure: Private Walking Tour | Theta Clinical Support">
  <div class="min-h-screen">
    <Header />
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white pt-24 pb-16">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
            Kichijoji Jazz Adventure
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-4">
            Private Walking Tour
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg opacity-90 mb-8">
            Escape the tourist crowds and discover Tokyo's beloved jazz neighborhood
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white/20 px-6 py-3 rounded-full">
              <span class="font-bold">4-6 hours</span> flexible duration
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/20 px-6 py-3 rounded-full">
              <span class="font-bold">Private tour</span> for your group
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/20 px-6 py-3 rounded-full">
              <span class="font-bold">English guide</span> with jazz expertise
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Kichijoji Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Why Kichijoji?</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              "This is exactly what I was looking for! I want to spend the whole week here!" - That's what visitors often say when they discover Kichijoji, especially after experiencing the tourist-heavy areas of Asakusa and Shibuya.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Kichijoji offers an authentic Tokyo experience where locals far outnumber tourists. It's a vibrant neighborhood with a thriving jazz scene, cozy record shops, intimate bars, and the charm of a small town within the big city.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Perfect for jazz lovers and anyone seeking the "real" Tokyo away from the crowds.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tour Highlights -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Tour Highlights</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-600">Jazz Venues & Music Culture</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• <strong>Strings</strong> - Live bar & Italian restaurant with nightly performances</li>
              <li>• <strong>Scratch</strong> - Historic jazz cafe/bar since 1974</li>
              <li>• <strong>Funky</strong> - Upstairs bar with great atmosphere</li>
              <li>• <strong>Hi Styles Records</strong> - Browse vinyl: jazz, funk, blues, soul</li>
              <li>• Hidden jazz kissaten (jazz cafes) known only to locals</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-600">Neighborhood Discoveries</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• <strong>Harmonica Yokocho</strong> - Tiny authentic izakaya alleys</li>
              <li>• <strong>Inokashira Park</strong> - Beautiful park, perfect for strolling</li>
              <li>• Local shotengai (shopping streets) with unique finds</li>
              <li>• Hidden shrines and neighborhood secrets</li>
              <li>• Authentic local eateries and cafes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
            <strong>Note:</strong> Venue availability varies by day and time. We'll create a custom itinerary based on what's open and happening during your visit. Live music schedules change weekly, but there's always something interesting to discover!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Optional Add-ons -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Optional Add-ons</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Ghibli Museum</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Visit the magical world of Studio Ghibli (advance tickets required)</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-bold">+¥3,000 per person</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">*Museum tickets not included</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Iseya Yakitori</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Historic yakitori restaurant by Inokashira Park since 1928</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-bold">+¥2,000 arrangement</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">*Food costs separate</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Extended Harmonica Yokocho</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Deep dive into the tiny izakaya alleys with food & drinks</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-bold">+¥5,000 per person</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">*Includes first round of drinks</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What's Included -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Tour Details</h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-600">What's Included</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>✓ Private English-speaking guide with jazz knowledge</li>
                <li>✓ Customized itinerary based on your interests</li>
                <li>✓ Venue recommendations and introductions</li>
                <li>✓ Local insights and cultural context</li>
                <li>✓ Flexible pace and route</li>
                <li>✓ Photo opportunities at best spots</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-600">What's Not Included</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>✗ Transportation costs (¥200-400 per person)</li>
                <li>✗ Food and drinks</li>
                <li>✗ Venue cover charges (if any)</li>
                <li>✗ Shopping purchases</li>
                <li>✗ Optional activity fees</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Meeting Point</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">JR Kichijoji Station<br>South Exit</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Duration</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">4-6 hours<br>(flexible)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Start Times</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">2:00 PM - 7:00 PM<br>(afternoon/evening)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-blue-50">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Tour Pricing</h2>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">Private Group Rates</h3>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-6">
              <table class="w-full mb-6">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b">
                    <th class="text-left py-3">Group Size</th>
                    <th class="text-right py-3">4 Hours</th>
                    <th class="text-right py-3">6 Hours</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr class="border-b">
                    <td class="py-3">1-2 people</td>
                    <td class="text-right font-bold">¥25,000</td>
                    <td class="text-right font-bold">¥35,000</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b">
                    <td class="py-3">3-4 people</td>
                    <td class="text-right font-bold">¥30,000</td>
                    <td class="text-right font-bold">¥42,000</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b">
                    <td class="py-3">5-6 people</td>
                    <td class="text-right font-bold">¥35,000</td>
                    <td class="text-right font-bold">¥49,000</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
              
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <p>• Prices are total for the entire group (not per person)</p>
                <p>• Children under 12 join free</p>
                <p>• Larger groups: please inquire</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Booking Form -->
    <section id="booking" class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Book Your Jazz Adventure</h2>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <form 
              class="space-y-6"
              name="jazz-tour-booking"
              method="POST"
              action="/tour-booking-success"
              data-netlify="true"
              data-netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
            >
              <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="jazz-tour-booking" />
              <div class="hidden">
                <label>
                  Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" />
                </label>
              </div>

              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                    Name <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                  </label>
                  <input 
                    type="text" 
                    name="name"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
                    required
                  />
                </div>
                
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                    Email <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                  </label>
                  <input 
                    type="email" 
                    name="email"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
                    required
                  />
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                    Preferred Date <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                  </label>
                  <input 
                    type="date" 
                    name="preferred_date"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
                    required
                  />
                </div>
                
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                    Alternative Date
                  </label>
                  <input 
                    type="date" 
                    name="alternative_date"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                    Group Size <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                  </label>
                  <select 
                    name="group_size"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
                    required
                  >
                    <option value="">Select group size</option>
                    <option value="1-2">1-2 people</option>
                    <option value="3-4">3-4 people</option>
                    <option value="5-6">5-6 people</option>
                    <option value="7+">7+ people (please specify in message)</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                    Tour Duration <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                  </label>
                  <select 
                    name="duration"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
                    required
                  >
                    <option value="">Select duration</option>
                    <option value="4 hours">4 hours</option>
                    <option value="6 hours">6 hours</option>
                    <option value="custom">Custom (please specify in message)</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                  Preferred Start Time
                </label>
                <select 
                  name="start_time"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
                >
                  <option value="">Select start time</option>
                  <option value="2:00 PM">2:00 PM</option>
                  <option value="3:00 PM">3:00 PM</option>
                  <option value="4:00 PM">4:00 PM</option>
                  <option value="5:00 PM">5:00 PM</option>
                  <option value="6:00 PM">6:00 PM</option>
                  <option value="7:00 PM">7:00 PM</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                  Optional Add-ons
                </label>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <label class="flex items-center">
                    <input type="checkbox" name="addons" value="ghibli" class="mr-2">
                    <span>Ghibli Museum (+¥3,000/person)</span>
                  </label>
                  <label class="flex items-center">
                    <input type="checkbox" name="addons" value="iseya" class="mr-2">
                    <span>Iseya Yakitori arrangement (+¥2,000)</span>
                  </label>
                  <label class="flex items-center">
                    <input type="checkbox" name="addons" value="harmonica" class="mr-2">
                    <span>Extended Harmonica Yokocho (+¥5,000/person)</span>
                  </label>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
                  Special Interests or Requests
                </label>
                <textarea 
                  rows="4"
                  name="message"
                  placeholder="Tell us about your jazz preferences, dietary restrictions, mobility needs, or any special requests"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
                ></textarea>
              </div>
              
              <button 
                type="submit"
                class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-4 px-6 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
              >
                Request Booking
              </button>

              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center">
                We'll confirm availability and send payment details within 24 hours
              </p>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Do I need to be a jazz expert?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Not at all! This tour is perfect for everyone from jazz newcomers to aficionados. Your guide will tailor explanations to your level of interest and knowledge.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">What if it rains?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Kichijoji is great in any weather! Most venues are indoors, and the covered shopping arcades provide shelter. We'll adjust the route as needed.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Can we buy vinyl records?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Absolutely! We'll visit record shops where you can browse and buy. Your guide can help with recommendations and shipping arrangements for larger purchases.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Is this tour wheelchair accessible?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Many venues in Kichijoji have stairs or narrow entrances. Please let us know about mobility needs when booking, and we'll create an accessible route focusing on barrier-free venues.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">What about dietary restrictions?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Kichijoji has options for most dietary needs. Let us know about allergies, vegetarian/vegan preferences, or other restrictions, and we'll plan accordingly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>